## Semantic Time

```
Step  → Move  → Quest  → Mission  → Journey
(atom)  (session)  (goal)   (transform)  (arc)
```

| Level | Name | What it is |
|-------|------|------------|
| Atomic | **Step** | The smallest action |
| Session | **Move** | A focused session |
| Goal | **Quest** | A mission with win condition |
| Transform | **Mission** | A transformational goal (quarter/year) |
| Arc | **Journey** | The hero's full path |

